divs: sighting detailsi was taking my mother home between 9 and 10 pm. i was driving down a winding road, cleared a curve, and ahead about 1\4 mile above and behind a stand of pine trees (edge of maclay gardens) was what looked exactly like the headlights of a jeep. i mean the lights were as big as jeep headlights coming at you 20 feet away. the lights were wobbling a bit and i thought it was moving forward, towards me. my thought was "that plane is about to hit those trees." i made a bend in the road and the lights were obscured for 1-2 second by trees. when i had a clear shot again, the lights were dipping down behind the trees. my car windows were closed, and when i saw the lights dipping i opened my window, but heard no sound. at that point i mentioned the lights to my mother, but she didn't see them. i came to the end of the road, turned left and kept looking in my mirrors to see them again, but did not. i have seen a few things that i wonder about, but this was was different, in that it was close and the lights were not small. had it been a helicoptor or plane, i would have heard it and\or it would have crashed into the trees.
Summary: Saw 2 bright headlight looking lights above and behind stand of trees
